Package: senado
Title: Access Data from the Brazilian Federal Senate Open Data API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Sidney", "da Silva Pereira Bissoli", , "sbissoli76@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a tidy interface to the Brazilian Federal Senate
    (Senado Federal) Open Data API. Functions return tibbles with
    standardized column names, automatic retry, caching, and rate
    limiting. Covers senators, votes, bills, committees, and more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/SidneyBissoli/senado
BugReports: https://github.com/SidneyBissoli/senado/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    cachem,
    cli,
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    rlang,
    tibble,
    xml2
